imdb.plot outline: From the classroom to the locker room to the kick-off each week, A Season With transports viewers behind-the-scenes, beyond the field and into the lives of student athletes as they compete throughout the season. Go deep inside the world of a different college football program each season, and follow the players and coaches as their respective season-long journeys unfold.
